2.40 Eastern time tomorrow,

00:33:59.000 --> 00:34:01.000
if you want to get to learn a little bit more

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:03.000
about what Genry is doing,

00:34:03.000 --> 00:34:05.000
I encourage you to go to Chris's talk as well.

00:34:06.000 --> 00:34:07.000
But one last question.

00:34:07.000 --> 00:34:09.000
I know we always ask this in the Hangout.

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:13.000
Is there a memorable piece of career advice

00:34:13.000 --> 00:34:16.000
that you've received over the course of your career

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:17.000
or that you've given to others

00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:19.000
that you'd like to share with us?

00:34:21.000 --> 00:34:23.000
Yes, now I'm just trying to think.

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:25.000
There's many different things I've been told over time.

00:34:26.000 --> 00:34:28.000
It's the positive thinking.

00:34:28.000 --> 00:34:33.000
So whenever I write, do writings,

00:34:33.000 --> 00:34:35.000
or whenever I try to communicate,

00:34:35.000 --> 00:34:38.000
I always try to do more of the positive spin of it.

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:39.000
So if there is a challenge,

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:41.000
like, well, you're learning from your challenges.

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:43.000
So every single challenge that happens,

00:34:43.000 --> 00:34:44.000
and that's why we use the word challenge too,

00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:47.000
instead of saying problem,

00:34:47.000 --> 00:34:48.000
because the challenge means that you have

00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:49.000
is an active piece

00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:51.000
where you can help us come up with a solution.

00:34:51.000 --> 00:34:53.000
But you always want to come with a positive spin with it

00:34:53.000 --> 00:34:57.000
because what is today is going to change tomorrow, right?

00:34:57.000 --> 00:35:00.000
So you always want to be able to find ways to improve yourself.

00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:03.000
And so the positive part of that

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.000
is always that there is always a tomorrow

00:35:05.000 --> 00:35:07.000
to be able to fix it.

00:35:08.000 --> 00:35:09.000
Thank you.

